name: Am I Normal ? (5)
description:
thank you for collecting 5 pieces of "am i normal ?"

life in this world is very suffocating, some people shout at me rudely as if I'm the devil, they only see the outside, even though I actually have a good personality, but I've never had a problem, let that lowly creature shout at me with any words, because that's what makes the difference from me and lowly creatures
